Change Log
~~~~~~~~~~

Date        Rev     Notes
----------- ------- -------------------------------------------------------
2005-11-14	2.0.1   - minor maintenance release, nothing functional changed

2005-08-09  2.0.0   - support for templated subject lines

2004-06-13  1.0.4   - bug fixes in short email pattern, scalar template
                      assignment

2004-06-12  1.0.3   - enhancements to email stripping routine (long form vs.
                      short form)

2004-06-07  1.0.2   - separated TWM_isValidEmail() from the class so it can
                      be more easily used externally

2004-06-04  1.0.1   - improvements to email regex

2004-06-04  1.0.0   - initial release

